Jesus, lover of my soul, Hide me, O my Savior, hide,Till the storm of life is past;
Safe into the haven guide; O receive my soul at last.

Lord Jesus! Hide me while the tempest still is high and while I am in the storm of life. O Lord Jesus, forgive me for all my sins! Lord just hide me in the shadow of your wing and never leave my side! I love You Lord!
